title: Rod Culleton loses appeal against bankruptcy verdict
text:
Map: Australia 
Former One Nation Senator Rod Culleton has lost an appeal against a Federal Court ruling declaring him bankrupt. 
Mr Culleton had fought the finding on several grounds, including that he was solvent when the ruling was made and that the matter should have gone before a jury. 
But the court has thrown out the case in the second legal loss for Mr Culleton today . 
This morning the High Court ruled his election was invalid because he was convicted of an offence at the time of the poll. 
More to come.
